{"type":null,"faqId":38992,"title":"手环如何恢复出厂设置？","answer":"<p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-indent:24.0pt;\nline-height:normal;\ntext-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other\"><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">手环恢复出厂设置有</span><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">种方法：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\n\"><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\n\"><span>1.<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">通过手环恢复出厂设置。</span><span style=\"\nline-height:150%;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">1</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">）滑动手环主界面找到</span><img style=\"vertical-align:middle;\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150908084940871001.png\"><span style=\"line-height:\n150%;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\"><span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">并点击进入；</span><span style=\"\nline-height:150%;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">2</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">）滑动手环屏幕找到并点击恢复出厂设置图标</span><img style=\"vertical-align:middle;\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150908084940163002.png\"><span style=\"line-height:150%;\nfont-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">；</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">3</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">）</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">点击手环屏幕上的</span><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\"> <b><span>√ </span></b></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">完成恢复出厂设置。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\n\"><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\n\"><span>2.<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">通过</span><span style=\"line-height:\n150%;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">APP</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">恢复出厂设置。手环和手机通过蓝牙正常连接时，打开</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">APP</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">，点击</span><img style=\"vertical-align:middle;\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150908084941668003.png\"><span style=\"line-height:\n150%;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\"><span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">进入手环设置菜单，点击“恢复出厂设置”，手环将恢复出厂设置。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-align:center;text-indent:24.0pt;\nline-height:normal;\ntext-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\nlayout-grid-mode:both;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150908084941810004.png\" style=\"width:227.25pt;height:137.25pt\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;line-height:normal;\ntext-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other\"><b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">说明：</span></b></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;line-height:normal;\ntext-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other\"><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">手环恢复出厂设置后，手环上的运动、睡眠和时间数据都会清零，再次使用时需要重新配对连接手机。</span></p>\n<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4302","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441673017000,"seriesProductName":"B0-Honor","visitedTimes":38,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}